snippet.title: Slime Rancher: Deluxe Edition AVAILABLE NOW!
snippet.description:
Slime Rancher: Deluxe Edition is now available on PS4 and Xbox One! You can pick it up at retail or shop.skybound.com! The Deluxe Edition includes all previous DLC with additional content:
* The Secret Style Pack
* Slimepedia booklet
* Original Soundtrack 1 + 2, and more!

Take home this wildly popular sandbox game to play anytime and never worry about losing your game in the cloud. Pick it up at retail stores or preorder the game at shop.skybound.com.
